194
00:10:37,042 --> 00:10:41,017
It was Basil who thought of it first.Basil was a little boy with impudent blue

195
00:10:41,017 --> 00:10:44,096
eyes and a turned-up nose, and Mary hatedhim.

196
00:10:44,096 --> 00:10:48,033
She was playing by herself under a tree,just as she had been playing the day the

197
00:10:48,033 --> 00:10:49,058
cholera broke out.

198
00:10:49,058 --> 00:10:53,077
She was making heaps of earth and paths fora garden and Basil came and stood near to

199
00:10:53,077 --> 00:10:56,479
