380
00:20:10,091 --> 00:20:15,039
Mary gave a little involuntary jump."Oh! did she die!" she exclaimed, quite

381
00:20:15,039 --> 00:20:16,068
without meaning to.

382
00:20:16,068 --> 00:20:20,073
She had just remembered a French fairystory she had once read called "Riquet a la

383
00:20:20,073 --> 00:20:21,019
Houppe."

