396
00:21:03,004 --> 00:21:06,098
She stared out of the window with her lipspinched together, and it seemed quite

397
00:21:06,098 --> 00:21:11,459
natural that the rain should have begun topour down in gray slanting lines and splash

398
00:21:11,459 --> 00:21:14,017
and stream down the window-panes.

399
00:21:14,017 --> 00:21:17,072
If the pretty wife had been alive she mighthave made things cheerful by being

400
00:21:17,072 --> 00:21:21,459
something like her own mother and byrunning in and out and going to parties as

