00:21:23,086 --> 00:21:27,769
But she was not there any more."You needn't expect to see him, because ten

403
00:21:27,769 --> 00:21:31,016
to one you won't," said Mrs. Medlock."And you mustn't expect that there will be

404
00:21:31,016 --> 00:21:31,099
people to talk to you.

405
00:21:31,099 --> 00:21:34,075
You'll have to play about and look afteryourself.

406
00:21:34,075 --> 00:21:38,035
You'll be told what rooms you can go intoand what rooms you're to keep out of.

407
00:21:38,035 --> 00:21:39,069
There's gardens enough.

408
00:21:39,069 --> 00:21:42,007
But when you're in the house don't gowandering and poking about.

