00:21:42,007 --> 00:21:44,063
Mr. Craven won't have it."

410
00:21:44,063 --> 00:21:49,035
"I shall not want to go poking about," saidsour little Mary and just as suddenly as

411
00:21:49,035 --> 00:21:53,003
she had begun to be rather sorry for Mr.Archibald Craven she began to cease to be

412
00:21:53,003 --> 00:21:57,085
sorry and to think he was unpleasant enoughto deserve all that had happened to him.

