00:21:57,085 --> 00:22:00,579
And she turned her face toward thestreaming panes of the window of the

414
00:22:00,579 --> 00:22:04,032
railway carriage and gazed out at the grayrain-storm which looked as if it would go

415
00:22:04,032 --> 00:22:06,519
on forever and ever.

416
00:22:06,519 --> 00:22:10,025
She watched it so long and steadily thatthe grayness grew heavier and heavier

417
00:22:10,025 --> 00:22:16,025
before her eyes and she fell asleep.

