2174
01:59:08,023 --> 01:59:11,939
There's nothin' he wouldn't do for th' sakeo' showin' off an' flirtin' his tail-

2175
01:59:11,939 --> 01:59:12,879
feathers.

2176
01:59:12,879 --> 01:59:15,061
