2177
01:59:15,061 --> 01:59:20,269
He very seldom talked much and sometimesdid not even answer Mary's questions except

2178
01:59:20,269 --> 01:59:24,079
by a grunt, but this morning he said morethan usual.

2179
01:59:24,079 --> 01:59:28,047
He stood up and rested one hobnailed booton the top of his spade while he looked her

2180
01:59:28,047 --> 01:59:31,048
over."How long has tha' been here?" he jerked

2181
01:59:31,048 --> 01:59:32,045
out.

