2186
01:59:44,065 --> 01:59:50,067
Thinks I to myself I never set eyes on anuglier, sourer faced young 'un."

2187
01:59:50,067 --> 01:59:54,379
Mary was not vain and as she had neverthought much of her looks she was not

2188
01:59:54,379 --> 01:59:57,059
greatly disturbed."I know I'm fatter," she said.

2189
01:59:57,059 --> 01:59:59,129
