2191
02:00:03,079 --> 02:00:07,038
There, indeed, was the robin, and shethought he looked nicer than ever.

2192
02:00:07,038 --> 02:00:11,057
His red waistcoat was as glossy as satinand he flirted his wings and tail and

2193
02:00:11,057 --> 02:00:15,699
tilted his head and hopped about with allsorts of lively graces.

2194
02:00:15,699 --> 02:00:18,199
He seemed determined to make BenWeatherstaff admire him.

2195
02:00:18,199 --> 02:00:22,065
But Ben was sarcastic."Aye, there tha' art!" he said.

2196
02:00:22,065 --> 02:00:27,021
"Tha' can put up with me for a bitsometimes when tha's got no one better.

2197
02:00:27,021 --> 02:00:31,058
